title: Against utilitarianism & consequentialism (within the vegan movement)
description: I'm amazed at how many "vegans" wanted to defend the practice of wearing leather, fur and even eating meat (within "veganism") with the single caveat that they acquired the product free of charge (2nd hand leather, 2nd hand morality).
